#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ", and feel free to"
msgstr ", ແລະ ສາມາດ... ໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. After placing your orders, look at our Kitchen Display. Click the "
"\"Backend\" menu in the right corner to return to your backend, then switch "
"to the Kitchen Display App."
msgstr ""
"1. ຫຼັງຈາກສັ່ງຊື້ແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງທີ່ໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົນໃນເຮືອນຄົວ. ຄລິກທີ່ເມນູ \"Backend\" ຢູ່ມຸມຂວາເພື່ອຄືນສູ່ລະບົ"
"ບຫຼັງບ້ານ, ຈາກນັ້ນປ່ຽນໄປໃຊ້ແອັບ Kitchen Display."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. First, create all your employees in the database. Navigate to the "
"Employee App to do so."
msgstr ""
"1. ທຳອິດ, ສ້າງພະນັກງານທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ. ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ແອັບພະນັກງານ (Employee App) ເພື່ອດຳເ"
"ນີນການ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Point of sale"
msgstr "1. ຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of sale)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. You are ready to welcome your first customers. To do so, select a table "
"on the floor map and select the products they asked for from the list."
msgstr ""
"1. ທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວທີ່ຈະຕ້ອນຮັບລູກຄ້າຄົນທຳອິດ. ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກໂຕະໃນແຜນຜັງ ແລະ ເລືອກສິນຄ້າທີ່ລູກ"
"ຄ້າຕ້ອງການຈາກລາຍການ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. Create your employees' roles under the \"Work Information\" tab. Some are"
" already created for this demo."
msgstr ""
"2. ສ້າງບົດບາດຂອງພະນັກງານພາຍໃຕ້ແຖບ \"ຂໍ້ມູນການເຮັດວຽກ\". ບາງບົດບາດໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນແລ້ວສຳລັບການສາ"
"ທິດນີ້."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Kiosks and self-ordering"
msgstr "2. ຕູ້ສັ່ງອາຫານ (Kiosks) ແລະ ການສັ່ງອາຫານດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. Open your preparation screen. Your orders are there. You can now mark "
"them as done either line by line or the entire order by clicking on the top."
msgstr ""
"2. ເປີດໜ້າຈໍການກຽມອາຫານ. ລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານຢູ່ທີ່ນັ້ນ. ທ່ານສາມາດໝາຍວ່າສຳເລັດແລ້ວ ໂດຍເລືອກເທື່ອລະ"
"ລາຍການ ຫຼື ທັງໝົດໂດຍການຄລິກຢູ່ด้านເທິງ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. To make it more interesting, feel free to create a second order. For this"
" one, select the \"Burger Menu Combo\" product. You can choose 2 burger "
"options burger options and 4 different drinks. This \"Combo\" feature will "
"allow you to create a menu with several courses and choices for each."
msgstr ""
"2. ເພື່ອໃຫ້ໜ້າສົນໃຈຂຶ້ນ, ລອງສ້າງລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ທີສອງ. ສຳລັບອັນນີ້, ໃຫ້ເລືອກສິນຄ້າ \"Burger Menu "
"Combo\". ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກເບີເກີໄດ້ 2 ແບບ ແລະ ເຄື່ອງດື່ມທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ 4 ຢ່າງ. ຄຸນສົມບັດ "
"\"Combo\" ນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສ້າງເມນູທີ່ມີຫຼາຍລາຍການ ແລະ ຫຼາຍຕົວເລືອກໃຫ້ແຕ່ລະຢ່າງ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. If you select Max Frite as a customer for your order, you can see that "
"there is a Loyalty Program running on your Point of Sale. Every money spent "
"provide a loyalty point, and 200 loyalty points give access to a free Combo "
"Menu."
msgstr ""
"3. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກ Max Frite ເປັນລູກຄ້າ, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່າມີແຜນງານສະສົມຄະແນນ (Loyalty Program) "
"ທີ່ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກຢູ່. ທຸກໆການໃຊ້ຈ່າຍຈະໄດ້ຮັບຄະແນນສະສົມ, ແລະ 200 ຄະແນນສາມາດແລກຊຸດ Combo ໄດ້ຟຣີ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Odoo provides your an order status display to let your customer see when "
"their order is ready. It is automatically setup and available by clicking "
"the \"Order status screen\" button on the preparation display."
msgstr ""
"3. Odoo ມີໜ້າຈໍສະແດງສະຖານະການສັ່ງຊື້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າເຫັນວ່າເມື່ອໃດອາຫານຂອງພວກເຂົາພ້ອມແລ້ວ. ມັນຖືກຕັ້ງ"
"ຄ່າໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ໜ້າຈໍສະຖານະການສັ່ງຊື້\" ໃນໜ້າຈໍການກຽມອາຫານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Preparation displays"
msgstr "3. ໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົນການກຽມອາຫານ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Return to the Planning App. You can see a few shifts ready to be planned."
" Select the down arrow next to the publish button and click \"Auto Plan.\" "
"Your shifts will be automatically assigned based on your employees' "
"availability."
msgstr ""
"3. ກັບໄປທີ່ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning App). ທ່ານຈະເຫັນບາງຜັດວຽກທີ່ພ້ອມຈະວາງແຜນ. ເລືອກລູກສອນລົ"
"ງຂ້າງປຸ່ມເຜີຍແຜ່ ແລະ ຄລິກ \"ວາງແຜນອັດຕະໂນມັດ (Auto Plan).\" ຜັດວຽກຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກມອບໝາຍໂດຍອັ"
"ດຕະໂນມັດຕາມຄວາມພ້ອມຂອງພະນັກງານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Replenishment"
msgstr "4. ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າໃນສາງ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. You can still reassign any shift to adapt the planning."
msgstr "4. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດມອບໝາຍຜັດວຽກໃໝ່ ເພື່ອປັບປ່ຽນການວາງແຜນໄດ້."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Once you are happy with it, send it to your co-workers by smashing the "
"publish button."
msgstr "5. ເມື່ອທ່ານພໍໃຈແລ້ວ, ສົ່ງໃຫ້ເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານຂອງທ່ານໂດຍການກົດປຸ່ມເຜີຍແຜ່."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "5. Plan your services"
msgstr "5. ວາງແຜນການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">⚠️</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">⚠️</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🎉</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🎉</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">💡</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">💡</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🔁</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🔁</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🚀</i>"
