msgstr "ຄະແນນສະສົມ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Make them pay the orders to release the table and continue your service."
msgstr "ໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາຊຳລະເງິນເພື່ອປ່ອຍໂຕະໃຫ້ວ່າງ ແລະ ດຳເນີນການບໍລິການຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage Loyalty Programs and many other kind of promotions, gifts and coupons"
" in the related page in your Point of Sales App &gt; Products."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການແຜນງານສະສົມຄະແນນ ແລະ ໂປຣໂມຊັ່ນຮູບແບບອື່ນໆ, ຂອງຂວັນ ແລະ ຄູປອງ ໃນໜ້າທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໃນແອັບຈຸດຂ"
"າຍ (POS) > ສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font"
" class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການທຸກຊ່ອງທາງການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານໃນບ່ອນດຽວດ້ວຍ Odoo <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງຄົມອອນລາຍ</font></strong>, ແລະ <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານ SMS</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage recurring tasks and never forget any replenishment or cleaning with "
"the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການວຽກທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນຊ້ຳໆ ແລະ ບໍ່ພາດການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ການເຮັດຄວາມສະອາດດ້ວຍ <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບໂຄງການ (Project App)</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ງ່າຍກວ່າທີ່ເຄີຍດ້ວຍລະບົບທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັນຢ່າງສົມບູນ. (<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບບັນຊີ</font></strong>)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo also provides easy self ordering possibilities. Print a specific QR "
"code for each table on your Point of Sale settings and allow your customer "
"to order directly on their mobile phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຍັງມີທາງເລືອກໃນການສັ່ງອາຫານດ້ວຍຕົນເອງທີ່ງ່າຍດາຍ. ພິມລະຫັດ QR ສະເພາະສຳລັບແຕ່ລະໂຕະໃນການຕັ້"
"ງຄ່າຈຸດຂາຍ ແລະ ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າສັ່ງອາຫານຜ່ານມືຖືຂອງພວກເຂົາໄດ້ໂດຍກົງ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" an additional cashier (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຖືກລວມເຂົ້າໃນແອັບດຽວຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດມັນເພື່ອປ່ຽນໂທລະສັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນເຄື່ອງຄິດເງິນເພີ່ມເຕີມ "
"(ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ)."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as :"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ສິ້ນສຸດໃຫ້ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ແມ່ນພຽງແຕ່ພາບລວມຂອງຄຸນສົມບັດໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລົບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ ແ"
"ລະ ທົດສອບທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"Receipt\" smart button to "
"validate your receipt and add these new products to your stock."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິນຄ້າມາຮອດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ໃບຮັບເຄື່ອງ (Receipt)\" ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນການຮັບ ແລະ ເພີ່ມສິນຄ້"
"າໃໝ່ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເຂົ້າໃນສາງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_2
msgid "Online Payment"
msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນອອນລາຍ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your customers easily with the<strong>"
" <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດງານກິດຈະກຳ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ແອັບກິດຈະກຳ (Events App)</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Plan your services easily using the Planning App."
msgstr ""
"ວາງແຜນການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍໂດຍໃຊ້ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning App)."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are displayed in the smart buttons on top of your product. "
"You can see a minimum quantity, and a maximum. Each time the forecast stock "
"lowers beneath the minimum stock, it automatically creates a purchase order "
"to replenish to the maximum quantity."
msgstr ""
"ກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ຈະສະແດງຢູ່ໃນປຸ່ມລັດດ້ານເທິງຂອງສິນຄ້າ. ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຈຳນວນຕ່ຳສຸດ ແລະ ສູງສຸດ. ທຸ"
"ກຄັ້ງທີ່ສິນຄ້າຄົງຄັງທີ່ຄາດການໄວ້ຫຼຸດລົງຕ່ຳກວ່າເກນຕ່ຳສຸດ, ລະບົບຈະສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອຕື່ມສິນຄ້າໃຫ້ຮອ"
"ດຈຳນວນສູງສຸດ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Replenishment is essential but challenging for a bar owner to systematize."
msgstr ""
"ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າຄືນແມ່ນສິ່ງຈຳເປັນ ແຕ່ເປັນສິ່ງທີ່ທ້າທາຍສຳລັບເຈົ້າຂອງບາໃນການເຮັດໃຫ້ເປັນລະບົບ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:product.template,name:fast_food.product_product_58_product_template
msgid "Sanitizer 250ml"
msgstr "ເຈລລ້າງມື 250 ມິນລີລິດ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:planning.role,name:fast_food.planning_role_1
msgid "Service"
msgstr "ບໍລິການ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_1
msgid "Sodexo Card Payment"
msgstr "ການຊຳລະດ້ວຍບັດ Sodexo"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kitchen Displays</font></strong> "
"will ensure a great follow-up of every order in your bar and kitchen."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົນໃນເຮືອນຄົວ</font></strong> ຈະຊ່"
"ວຍໃຫ້ການຕິດຕາມທຸກລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ໃນບາ ແລະ ເຮືອນຄົວຂອງທ່ານມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The kiosk layout is optimized for vertical usage, as most booths use that "
"kind of display."
msgstr ""
"ຮູບແບບຂອງຕູ້ສັ່ງອາຫານ (Kiosk) ຖືກປັບໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບການໃຊ້ງານໃນແນວຕັ້ງ, ເນື່ອງຈາກບູດສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ໃຊ້ໜ້າຈໍຮູ"
"ບແບບນັ້ນ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The stock is only updated when you close your register. Let's do it before "
"continuing to the next step."
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າໃນສາງຈະຖືກອັບເດດເມື່ອທ່ານປິດຮອບການຂາຍເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ໃຫ້ເຮັດຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້ກ່ອນຈະໄປຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr "ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນໃຊ້ໄດ້ຟຣີໃນແພັກເກັດປັດຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ເຊີນທົດລອງໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use case:"
msgstr "ກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງ:"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory App</font></strong>"
" to manage your stock and receive products."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory App)</font></"
"strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການສາງ ແລະ ຮັບສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning App</font></strong> "
"to schedule and share your shifts with your employees."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning App)</font>"
"</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດຕາຕະລາງ ແລະ ແບ່ງປັນຜັດວຽກກັບພະນັກງານຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale</font></strong>"
" at the desk for your sales. You can also download the Odoo Mobile App on "
"any phone to take orders. And create <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Kiosks </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">or QR Codes</span></font></strong> to ensure self-"
"ordering."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale)</font></"
"strong> ຢູ່ທີ່ໂຕະສຳລັບການຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດດາວໂຫລດ ແອັບ Odoo ເທິງມືຖື ໃນໂທລະສັບທຸກລຸ້ນເ"
"ພື່ອຮັບລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້. ແລະ ສ້າງ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຕູ້ບໍລິການ </font>"
"<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">ຫຼື QR "
"Codes</span></font></strong> ເພື່ອຮອງຮັບການສັ່ງຊື້ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App</font></strong> "
"to reorder your products."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ (Purchase App)</font></"
"strong> ເພື່ອສັ່ງຊື້ສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານຄືນໃໝ່."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:fast_food.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການທົດລອງໃຊ້."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ສຶກສາເພີ່ມເຕີມບໍ່?"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily edit the floor map by clicking \"Edit plan\" in the top-right"
" menu when on the table selection step of your Point of Sale."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮ້ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍໂດຍຄລິກ \"ແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງ (Edit plan)\" ໃນເມນູຂວາມືດ້ານເ"
"ທິງ ເມື່ອຢູ່ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນການເລືອກໂຕະຂອງຈຸດຂາຍ (POS)."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now email your Request for Proposal to your vendor or confirm it "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງອີເມວການຂໍໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໄປຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໄດ້."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that there is a reordering rule configured for this product if "
"you go to Inventory &gt; Products &gt; Blond Beer"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ສຳລັບສິນຄ້ານີ້ ຫາກທ່ານໄປທີ່ ສາງສິນຄ້າ > ສິນຄ້າ > "
"Blond Beer"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດການທົດລອງກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງນີ້ແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີໃນການປັບແຕ່ງ Odoo ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້"
"ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດທ່ານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You currently have two steps in your Kitchen Displays: one for the "
"kitchen/bar and one for the service. You can configure steps in the kitchen "
"display configuration menu."
msgstr ""
"ປັດຈຸບັນທ່ານມີສອງຂັ້ນຕອນໃນໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົນໃນເຮືອນຄົວ: ອັນໜຶ່ງສຳລັບເຮືອນຄົວ/ບາ ແລະ ອີກອັນໜຶ່ງສຳລັບການບໍລິກ"
"ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຂັ້ນຕອນຕ່າງໆໄດ້ໃນເມນູການຕັ້ງຄ່າໜ້າຈໍເຮືອນຄົວ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Fast Food Restaurant package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ່? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ > Industries > Upgrade ແພັກເກັດ "
"Fast Food Restaurant ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have two main possibilities in Odoo to ease your replenishment process."
msgstr "ທ່ານມີສອງທາງເລືອກຫຼັກໃນ Odoo ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Fast Food Restaurant package. By doing so, "
"we have installed many necessary apps to run your restaurant efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຫາກໍ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແພັກເກັດ Odoo ສຳລັບຮ້ານອາຫານຟາດຟູດ. ດ້ວຍເຫດນີ້, ພວກເຮົາຈຶ່ງໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນຫຼາຍຢ່"
"າງເພື່ອໃຫ້ຮ້ານອາຫານຂອງທ່ານດຳເນີນງານໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various actions you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນຈະສາມາດລອງເຮັດຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງການເຮັດວຽກຕ່າງໆ ທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າ"
"ງວ່ອງໄວດ້ວຍແພັກເກັດນີ້."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your demo database comes with a kiosk to allow your customer to take orders "
"on your booths. Go to the Point of Sale App and select your kiosk to see how"
" it looks and try it!"
msgstr ""
"ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງທ່ານມາພ້ອມກັບລະບົບຕູ້ສັ່ງອາຫານ (Kiosk) ເພື່ອໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າສັ່ງອາຫານເອງໄດ້. ໄປທີ່ແອັບຈຸດຂ"
"າຍ (POS) ແລະ ເລືອກ Kiosk ຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອເບິ່ງ ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your orders will automatically move from a step to another while you move it"
" on your preparation display."
msgstr ""
"ລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານຈະຍ້າຍຈາກຂັ້ນຕອນໜຶ່ງໄປຫາອີກຂັ້ນຕອນໜຶ່ງໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເມື່ອທ່ານຍ້າຍມັນໃນໜ້າຈໍການກຽມ"
"ອາຫານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "academy"
msgstr "ສະຖາບັນ (academy)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "and"
msgstr "ແລະ"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຄູ່ມື"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "if you need help! <br/>"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ! <br/>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "request a demo"
msgstr "ຂໍເບິ່ງຕົວຢ່າງການໃຊ້ງານ"
